---
import Arrow from "../../assets/pointer-arrow.svg";
---

<section class="overview">
  <div id="services">
    <ul>
      <li>
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Separation</h3>
        <p>
          We guide you through separation with practical and emotional support,
          assisting with early decisions around parenting, living arrangements
          and finances, and helping you move forward with clarity, stability and
          confidence during a challenging transition.
        </p>
        <span
          ><a href="/services/separation"
            >Learn more<img src=`${Arrow.src}` /></a
          ></span
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Divorce</h3>
        <p>
          We support you through the divorce process from start to finish,
          assisting with eligibility, paperwork and court requirements, or
          supported DIY applications, to help you finalise your divorce with
          confidence, efficiency and peace of mind.
        </p>
        <span
          ><a href="/services/divorce">Learn more<img src=`${Arrow.src}` /></a
          ></span
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Parenting matters</h3>
        <p>
          We help develop clear, child focused parenting arrangements covering
          living schedules, decision making, communication and safety, using
          negotiation, mediation and strong documentation to reduce conflict and
          support stability for children and parents alike.
        </p>
        <span
          ><a href="/services/parenting-matters"
            >Learn more<img src=`${Arrow.src}` /></a
          ></span
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Property and financial settlements</h3>
        <p>
          We assist with fair property settlements, including assets,
          liabilities and superannuation, offering practical advice and skilled
          negotiation to manage both simple and complex matters and secure
          legally binding outcomes that protect your financial future.
        </p>
        <span
          ><a href="/services/property-and-financial-settlements"
            >Learn more<img src=`${Arrow.src}` /></a
          ></span
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Child support</h3>
        <p>
          We assist with child support and adult maintenance matters, including
          assessments, agreements and disputes, ensuring financial arrangements
          meet legal requirements, reflect your childâ€™s needs and are managed
          with clear, practical and straightforward guidance.
        </p>
        <span
          ><a href="/services/child-support"
            >Learn more<img src=`${Arrow.src}` /></a
          ></span
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Maintenance</h3>
        <p>
          We provide clear advice on spousal maintenance after separation,
          including eligibility, time limits and entitlements, assisting with
          preparing or responding to claims and achieving outcomes tailored to
          your financial circumstances and future needs.
        </p>
        <span
          ><a href="/services/maintenance"
            >Learn more<img src=`${Arrow.src}` /></a
          ></span
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Financial Agreements</h3>
        <p>
          We prepare, review and negotiate Financial Agreements that define how
          assets, liabilities and maintenance will be managed, ensuring legal
          compliance, informed decision making and long term certainty and
          protection for both parties.
        </p>
        <span
          ><a href="/services/financial-agreements"
            >Learn more<img src=`${Arrow.src}` /></a
          ></span
        >
      </li>
    </ul>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <h3>LGBTIQA+ family law</h3>
        <p>
          We provide inclusive, respectful family law support for LGBTQIA+
          individuals and families, assisting with separation, parenting,
          property and child support matters, while offering strong advocacy,
          clear advice and a safe, affirming legal environment.
        </p>
        <span
          ><a href="/services/lgbtiqa-family-law"
            >Learn more<img src=`${Arrow.src}` /></a
          ></span
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Neurodivergent family support</h3>
        <p>
          We offer neurodiversity informed family law services, tailoring
          parenting arrangements, communication strategies and processes to
          respect sensory, emotional and practical needs, while promoting
          understanding, flexibility and outcomes that support long term family
          wellbeing.
        </p>
        <span
          ><a href="/services/neurodivergent-family-support"
            >Learn more<img src=`${Arrow.src}` /></a
          ></span
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Family violence intervention</h3>
        <p>
          We support individuals affected by family violence, assisting with
          intervention orders and related parenting and property matters,
          prioritising safety, clear advice and strong representation to help
          protect your wellbeing and legal interests.
        </p>
        <span
          ><a href="/services/family-violence-intervention"
            >Learn more<img src=`${Arrow.src}` /></a
          ></span
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>De facto relationship law</h3>
        <p>
          We advise clients in de facto relationships on their legal rights and
          responsibilities, including property settlement, maintenance and
          financial agreements, providing clear guidance and support through
          negotiations, documentation and court processes when required.
        </p>
        <span
          ><a href="/services/de-facto-relationship-law"
            >Learn more<img src=`${Arrow.src}` /></a
          ></span
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Family Dispute Resolution (mediation)</h3>
        <p>
          We facilitate structured family dispute resolution for parenting and
          property matters, led by an accredited practitioner who supports
          respectful communication, safety focused discussions and practical
          agreements designed to resolve issues without court intervention.
        </p>
        <span
          ><a href="/services/family-dispute-resolution-mediation"
            >Learn more<img src=`${Arrow.src}` /></a
          ></span
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Trauma-informed client care</h3>
        <p>
          We deliver trauma-informed legal support focused on emotional safety,
          predictability and clarity, using sensitive communication, paced
          processes and collaborative approaches to minimise distress and
          support clients navigating complex family law matters.
        </p>
        <span
          ><a href="/services/trauma-informed-client-care"
            >Learn more<img src=`${Arrow.src}` /></a
          ></span
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Mental-health-centred wellbeing support</h3>
        <p>
          We prioritise wellbeing for clients and our team by fostering a
          supportive environment, clear communication and access to trusted
          professionals, ensuring a compassionate, balanced legal experience
          throughout your family law journey.
        </p>
        <span
          ><a href="/services/mental-health-centred-wellbeing-support"
            >Learn more<img src=`${Arrow.src}` /></a
          ></span
        >
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

